# Pricing Section (.vasora)

components:
  - name: pricing-grid
    description: "Responsive pricing tier cards with toggle for monthly/yearly and recommended badge."
    props:
      - tiers: array
      - billingCycle: string # 'monthly' | 'yearly'

accessibility:
  - ensure tariff cards are keyboard-focusable (tabindex=0)
  - use aria-pressed for billing toggle and aria-live for price updates
  - contrast: follow WCAG AA for text and button colors

assets-suggestions:
  - assets/vasora/icon-recommended.svg
  - assets/vasora/pricing-illustration-1.svg

notes:
  - animation: prefer reduced-motion preference respect (prefers-reduced-motion)
  - pricing copy: include small legal text area for VAT and trial info
